messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "reason": "原始意图API返回的raw_intent为'4001'，未被识别为customer_portrait"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "reason": "适配层将raw_intent'4001'映射为'other'，未能映射到'customer_portrait'"
        },
        {
          "stage": "label_mapping",
          "reason": "标签映射维持'other'，未回退到正确意图"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别服务对用户查询'帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？'未能正确识别为customer_portrait，返回了意图编码'4001'，随后适配层和映射层均未能纠正，导致最终意图标签为other。可能的原因包括：意图分类模型未充分学习customer_portrait的语义特征，或'4001'编码被错误映射。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "input_query": "帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？"
        },
        {
          "expected_intent": "customer_portrait"
        },
        {
          "actual_intent": "other"
        },
        {
          "raw_intent": "4001"
        },
        {
          "intent_api_call_endpoint": "/api/v1/marketing-planning/intent-recognition"
        },
        {
          "adapter_extraction_output": {
            "intent": "other",
            "confidence": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "intent_contract_probe": {
            "expected_intent": "customer_portrait",
            "actual_intent": "other",
            "evidence_intent": "4001",
            "intent_match": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "提取目标产品实体为重疾险",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "reason": "意图识别API未返回target_value实体"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "reason": "适配层输出target_value为null，未从响应中提取到产品实体"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别服务未能从用户查询中抽取出产品实体'重疾险'，导致适配层输出的target_value为null。这可能是因为实体抽取模块未能识别该产品名称，或识别流程未将产品信息作为required slot输出。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "expected_target_value": "重疾险"
        },
        {
          "actual_target_value": null
        },
        {
          "intent_evidence": {
            "slots": {},
            "entities": []
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度达到可信水平",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "reason": "API返回的置信度为0.5，低于0.7"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "reason": "适配层传递了低置信度，未进行阈值校验或提升"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别API对本次查询给出的置信度为0.5，低于0.7的可信阈值，表明模型对判断结果信心不足。可能由于训练数据覆盖不足或查询模糊，导致模型无法做出高置信度预测。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "actual_confidence": 0.5
        },
        {
          "expected_min_confidence": 0.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {
          "stage": "intent_api_call",
          "reason": "意图识别输出与合同不一致"
        },
        {
          "stage": "adapter_extraction",
          "reason": "映射导致最终输出偏离合同"
        }
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别链路未能满足reference contract：期望intent=customer_portrait且target_value=重疾险，实际intent=other、target_value=null、confidence=0.5，整体未通过合同校验。",
      "evidence": [
        {
          "contract": {
            "expected_intent": "customer_portrait",
            "expected_target_value": "重疾险"
          }
        },
        {
          "actual_output": {
            "intent": "other",
            "target_value": null,
            "confidence": 0.5
          }
        },
        {
          "judge_result": "fulfillment not met, blocking"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {
      "stage": "intent_api_call",
      "reason": "源头错误：意图识别API返回错误的意图编码和较低的置信度，且未提取产品实体"
    },
    {
      "stage": "adapter_extraction",
      "reason": "适配层将原始编码错误映射为other，未能提供回退或纠正机制"
    },
    {
      "stage": "label_mapping",
      "reason": "标签映射未检测到与期望contract的偏离，直接输出other"
    }
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "单轮意图识别链路的根因在于intent_api_call阶段，意图识别服务未能将用户查询正确分类为customer_portrait，并遗漏了产品实体，导致下游适配和映射全部错误。置信度低进一步表明模型对该意图的区分能力不足。需要检查意图识别模型/服务的训练数据、prompt配置以及实体抽取规则，确保涉及客户画像和产品词的查询被正确识别。",
  "evidence": [
    {
      "description": "用户查询",
      "value": "帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？"
    },
    {
      "description": "期望意图与实体",
      "value": "intent=customer_portrait, target_value=重疾险"
    },
    {
      "description": "实际输出",
      "value": "intent=other, target_value=null, confidence=0.5"
    },
    {
      "description": "原始API返回的编码",
      "value": "raw_intent=4001"
    },
    {
      "description": "意图映射检查",
      "value": "runtime_checks intent_mapping failed, expected customer_portrait but got other"
    },
    {
      "description": "合同对比",
      "value": "intent_contract_probe intent_match=false, evidence_intent=4001"
    }
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

